body:
GCC-nm-11

NAME

gcc-nm - a wrapper around nm adding the --plugin option

SYNOPSIS

gcc-nm [ OPTION ] ... [ ARGS ...]

DESCRIPTION

gcc-nm is a wrapper around nm(1) adding the appropriate --plugin option for the GCC 11 compiler.

OPTIONS

See nm(1) for a list of options that nm understands.

SEE ALSO

nm(1)
